reviewText:
Seeing this video is a priviledge. Hats off to the makers of this video. They have done an amazing scientific analysis of the predators. Equipped with tools bestowed upon them by nature the predators are shown to maintain the ecosystem and live in harmony with it. No doubt this video won 3 international awards.

Highly highly recommended for any avid wild life fan.

Anybody who sees this video will conceed that God is the greatest scientist of all.
